Dedicated virtual machine hosts let user  run Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Compute virtual machine (VM) instances on dedicated servers that are a single tenant and not shared with other customers.
#  Prerequisites:
#  Shape:
#  supported shape for dedicated vm host :
#  DVH.Standard2.52
#  DVH.Standard3.64
#  DVH.Standard.E2.64
#  DVH.Standard.E3.128
#  DVH.Standard.E4.128
#  DVH.DenseIO2.52
#  DVH.Optimized3.36